DataElement.preferredName: Study Research Resource Primary Flag ISO21090.BL.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: Specifies whether this is the main or principal study resource. EXAMPLE(S): This distinguishes between an organization that is the primary funder vs. a funder who provides less money for a study.

The indicator usually takes the form of a single binary digit, or bit (either 0 or 1). (from Dictionary of Computers)
